content:
Assign the Workforce Engagement Analyst, Workforce Engagement Planner, or Workforce Engagement Agent permission sets to users of Workforce Engagement features.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience and in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

Workforce Engagement User Permission Sets:

* Workforce Engagement Analyst: Can create and adjust workload histories, intelligent forecasts, and capacity plans.
* Workforce Engagement Planner: Can create, adjust, schedule shifts from capacity plans; perform schedule-related tasks like batch assignment or get candidates.
* Workforce Engagement Agent: Can request time off, submit time sheets, create service resource preferences, receive email notifications from Intraday Management, and view agent home.
title: Assigning Workforce Engagement User Permission Sets
